# zero-touchd-standalone user store — one record per line:
#   <id>:<sha256-hex-of-password>:<Admin|Viewer>
#
# The password is stored ONLY as its lowercase sha256 hex; the daemon hashes the
# incoming SMS password and compares. Admin is required for mutating commands
# (GNMI SET / APN / RADIO RESTART / REBOOT); Viewer may GNMI GET / STATUS.
#
# Generate a hash:   printf '%s' 'your-password' | sha256sum
#
